---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.endsWith('/') ? import.meta.env.BASE_URL : `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/`;
---

<Layout 
  title="About Us | One Smile Dental Care"
  description="Learn about One Smile Dental Care, led by Dr. Radhika. Discover our philosophy, qualifications, and state-of-the-art dental technology."
>
  <section class="py-20 bg-stone-900 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_center,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-teal-950/40 via-stone-950 to-stone-950 opacity-90 z-0"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center py-10">
      <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-400">Our Story</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mt-3 mb-6">About Our Clinic</h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-stone-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light">
        A state-of-the-art dental studio built on trust, advanced sterilization, and personalized patient care.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Philosophy Section */}
  <section class="py-20 bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-600">The One Smile Standard</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-stone-900 leading-tight">Patient-Centric Dental Excellence</h2>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            At One Smile Dental Care, we believe that dental visits should be transparent, painless, and focused on lifetime wellness. Our studio is custom-tailored to provide a calm, welcoming atmosphere where you are actively involved in your dental journey.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            We follow international Class-B sterilization protocols, utilizing high-pressure autoclaves to ensure 100% sterile tools. We are also one of the few clinics in the region to integrate a dedicated water purification system specifically for dental units to prevent bacterial contamination.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-video w-full shadow-lg border border-stone-200 bg-stone-100">
          <img 
            src={`${base}clinic/treating-patient.jpg`} 
            alt="Sterile dental care room showing patient treatment setup" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Dr Radhika Profile */}
  <section class="py-20 bg-stone-100 border-t border-b border-stone-200">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 relative">
          <div class="aspect-[3/4] w-full rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-stone-200 shadow-xl relative">
            <img 
              src={`${base}doctors/docot-radhika-2.jpg`} 
              alt="Dr. Radhika smiling" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-stone-900/60 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 text-white z-10">
              <div class="text-lg font-bold">Dr. Radhika</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-teal-400 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Lead Surgeon & Restorative Architect</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col gap-6">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-600">Lead Practitioner</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-stone-900">Dr. Radhika</h2>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            Dr. Radhika brings advanced surgical and cosmetic training to One Smile Dental Care. With a focus on dental implants, endodontics, and complex smile makeovers, she is dedicated to executing precise, long-lasting dental work.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            She regularly participates in continuing education programs worldwide, ensuring that One Smile patients benefit from the latest developments in digital dental dentistry and pain-free treatment options.
          </p>
          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-teal-500 pl-4 italic text-stone-700 font-medium my-2">
            "A healthy, radiant smile has the power to transform a person's life, health, and self-confidence. That transformation is what motivates us every single day."
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Advanced Technology Section */}
  <section class="py-20 bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-stone-900 mb-4">Our Technology</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-stone-600">
          We invest in advanced dental technology to guarantee maximum diagnostic accuracy, safety, and patient comfort.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        
        {/* Tech item 1 */}
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-full sm:w-36 aspect-video sm:aspect-square shrink-0 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-stone-100">
            <img 
              src={`${base}clinic/ster.jpg`} 
              alt="Medical autoclave sterilization machinery" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-stone-900">Autoclave Class-B Sterilization</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
              We employ professional-grade autoclave devices to perform vacuum steam sterilization of all instruments, eradicating 100% of bacterial and viral spores.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Tech item 2 */}
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-full sm:w-36 aspect-video sm:aspect-square shrink-0 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-stone-100">
            <img 
              src={`${base}clinic/wtarepurif.webp`} 
              alt="Water purification filters and tanks" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-stone-900">Pure Water Unit Integration</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
              Our dental chairs run on a closed-loop pure water filtration system, ensuring that the water used in your mouth during procedures is free of microbes.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Tech item 3 */}
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-full sm:w-36 aspect-video sm:aspect-square shrink-0 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-stone-100">
            <img 
              src={`${base}clinic/xray.jpg`} 
              alt="Digital dental xray machine" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-stone-900">High-Precision Digital X-Rays</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
              Digital radiography exposes you to up to 90% less radiation than traditional film, producing instant, high-contrast images for precise treatment planning.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Tech item 4 */}
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-full sm:w-36 aspect-video sm:aspect-square shrink-0 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-stone-100">
            <img 
              src={`${base}clinic/tools.jpg`} 
              alt="Advanced dental surgical and examination tools" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-stone-900">Rotary Endodontic Systems</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
              We use electric rotary tools for root canal treatments, resulting in faster treatments, quieter appointments, and a pain-free experience.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
